          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "A string describing the width at which Apple News displays the article. The value indicates whether iOS considers the article width constrained (",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "compact",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ") or expansive (r",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "egular",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": "). When Apple News displays the article at the specified size class, the conditional properties are in effect. The horizontal size class is always ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "regular",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " in macOS.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
